thread.title_full: OptiContacts.com reviewed by STEPHANIE BENNETT SMITH

author: STEPHANIE BENNETT SMITH
title: STEPHANIE BENNETT SMITH
text: Affordable prices with quick shipping! I appreciate the ease of uploading my prescription for verification. More importantly, you can't beat snagging a box of contacts for $15.00 when it normally cost me $45.00 per box.
